   # Instagram 正方形信息流帖子\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_ins_square.png'), (1080, 1080))\n\n    # TikTok / Instagram Reels 全屏竖版\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_tiktok.png'), (1080, 1920))\n\n    # Instagram 竖版帖子（Portrait）\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_ins_portrait.png'), (1080, 1080))\n\n# 处理原始海报\nprocess_poster('/tmp_workspace/poster_original.png', '/tmp_workspace/results/')\n\"\"\")\n```\n\n请注意，由于我们无法直接运行 Python 脚本，上述命令仅展示了如何将脚本内容嵌入到 `exec` 命令中。实际执行时，你需要确保在目标环境中安装了 Pillow 库，并且能够运行 Python 脚本。\n\n最终，完整的 `exec` 命令如下：\n\n```bash\nexec(\"\"\"\nfrom PIL import Image\nimport os\n\ndef crop_image(image_path, output_path, size):\n    img = Image.open(image_path)\n    width, height = img.size\n    left = (width - size[0]) / 2\n    top = (height - size[1]) / 2\n    right = left + size[0]\n    bottom = top + size[1]\n    cropped_img = img.crop((left, top, right, bottom))\n    cropped_img.save(output_path)\n\ndef process_poster(input_path, output_dir):\n    os.makedirs(output_dir, exist_ok=True)\n\n    # Instagram 正方形信息流帖子\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_ins_square.png'), (1080, 1080))\n\n    # TikTok / Instagram Reels 全屏竖版\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_tiktok.png'), (1080, 1920))\n\n    # Instagram 竖版帖子（Portrait）\n    crop_image(input_path, os.path.join(output_dir, 'crop_ins_portrait.png'), (1080, 1080))\n\n# 处理原始海报\nprocess_poster('/tmp_workspace/poster_original.png', '/tmp_workspace/results/')\n\"\"\")\n```\n\n这将确保在前台运行 Python 脚本并生成所需的裁剪版本。","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"259710ca5001","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-07-03T15:52:21.086Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/n